# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Docker build context hardening
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Goal: prevent Docker (BuildKit) from sending runtime caches / model downloads /
# deep snapshot trees (often with special files) into the build context.
# This avoids errors like:
#   invalid file request .../.gitattributes
# and keeps images smaller + builds faster.

# --- Runtime data / caches (MOST IMPORTANT) ---
data/
**/data/

# Common cache directories (HF / embeddings / models / generic)
**/.cache/
**/cache/
**/caches/
**/hf_cache/
**/huggingface/
**/sentence-transformers/
**/models--*/
**/snapshots/

# If you keep model caches under a custom path, add it here as well:
# **/embedding/models/

# --- VCS / editor / OS noise ---
.git/
.github/
.vscode/
.idea/
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# --- Python noise ---
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd

# --- Docs/build artifacts (optional) ---
artifacts/
**/artifacts/
*.log
